reviews.text: I got the beef noodle soup, which was okay. Not that great compared to what I am used to getting in Taiwan. The soup was not as flavorful and the spiciness was more of a white pepper type spicy, rather than a flavorful chili spicy. I got the shank and it was sliced somewhat thinly - again not the typical style in Taiwan.

Not sure if this is authentic Taiwanese seems modified cuisine to me. Staff were super friendly compared with the average Hong Kong style service (you know what I mean). They have a long list of Taiwanese drinks which is awesome.

Taiwanese restaurant, service is speedy and the food is reasonable priced. The menu is on a slip of paper so you can make your decision while waiting for your table. A bit of a line up during weekday lunch hour. The restaurant is not very big so expect cosy seating. It's a good place for quick lunches.
Taiwanese fast food and drinks. Nice owner and hardworking staff. But never been super impressed by the food here which is very average.

Famous Taiwanese restaurant which is supposed to be authentic & yummy. I have tried the beef noodle of which the soup tasted ok, a bit spicy & lack rich beef flavour. Beef was tender but seemingly not freshly cooked today. The winter melon drink was too sweet but nothing special. There are better Taiwanese beef noodle elsewhere in HK. Service was quite though.

reviews.text:
襯著媽媽不煮飯加上第2天是假期就打算去中環找好吃的 ...
在網上搜尋餐廳時看到 - 吃什麼 WHAT TO EAT ~
這家名字很特別便提起了興趣

是說不知為何一進店就聞到奇怪味道，大概是某些醬汁?!
另外近門口位置看到一箱箱水果 .___. 沒想到台灣料理餐廳也賣水果呢
晚餐時間的話~客人頗多是需要搭枱的喔
也沒有餐牌，直接看下單紙和自己劃單那樣子~

滷肉飯($42/小碗) -說是小碗，其實份量來說也不算小。
只是飯量頗足，就是滷肉和汁看起來較少吧
整個偏惹味，滷肉是半肥瘦的那種還不錯～
原味蛋餅($35) & 起司蛋餅 ($39)
兩者的味道也很淡...但勉強還是能吃到蛋味吧 ...
口感來說還可以，不過起司那個連鹹香也吃不到的話有點難以理解 ...

椒鹽雞腿很香 看到別人吃所以也跟著點....但皮脆肉好乾😖😖😖一點都不好吃！
鮪魚蛋餅看起來很紮實....但鮪魚好乾 整塊不知道在嚼什麼～
本來很期待來吃 撲了一次空 這次還想說終於有開店.....結果特別失望😫😫😫
價錢還真的挺貴的...可能中環租金特高吧⋯⋯

I got the beef noodle soup, which was okay. Not that great compared to what I am used to getting in Taiwan. The soup was not as flavorful and the spiciness was more of a white pepper type spicy, rather than a flavorful chili spicy. I got the shank and it was sliced somewhat thinly - again not the typical style in Taiwan.

好友相約中環食飯，又無揀定食乜下😥走到黎大館附近，見到未到12點已經有人排隊既what to eat? 😊

小店裝修幾靚，但係位置超窄，係坐得唔太舒服😑😑 點菜都係飛紙仔，主力係台式飯🍚麵🍝，嗌咗個椒鹽雞腿飯，一個荔枝🍒冰茶同火腿🐷蛋🍳餅😬

嘢飲先上，朋友既珍奶個樣👌 我杯荔枝冰茶就係好甜同好甜，台式飲品大概都係咁😐

兩個雞腿🍗飯上枱，個賣相真係幾💞💓 蛋，清瓜，雞腿整齊地將飯面分為三等份，然後下面仲有少許肉燥

不過一筆落去就知太流，啲飯既份量明顯比其他台式舖少😣 雞腿其實都唔大枝，肉質還算👌 個瓜就烚咗上枱，同平時台式飯，成碗都濃烈醬味既客家風有啲唔同

飯差唔多食完，店員就趕住黎收嘢，似係趕枱，但其實個蛋餅都仲未上😑😑 食完再等咗 5，6分鐘蛋餅先黎，賣相一樣👌 食落嘛，火腿還火腿，蛋還蛋，皮還皮，唔係難食，但吾太深刻😬食到最後一舊都未食完，嘢飲又未飲晒，店員又埋黎問收得未。。。呢啲趕枱真係好倒胃口

埋單價錢130一位咁滯，有力氣行遠啲食豬飯會開心少少，加埋又窄又趕枱，味道又一般，無下次👎

Not sure if this is authentic Taiwanese seems modified cuisine to me. Staff were super friendly compared with the average Hong Kong style service (you know what I mean). They have a long list of Taiwanese drinks which is awesome.

result.name: Tango Argentinian Steak House

reviews.text: Come here few times a year whenever we have an excuse for a "special occasion", never a bad meal and always happy and satisfied with the food and service. Have tried almost all the steak selection and platters including the lamb (which is just as good as the beef by the way) except for the bone in sirloin. Steaks are always cooked to perfection, appetizers (sweetbread and melted cheese especially) are fantastic and desserts are on point. They also serve great bread.

I'm from Europe. There aren't many steakhouse having steak with the real steak taste.
This is one of the restaurant has.
Minus just one star. Because the meat was little too fat.
Ant little bit overpriced. -15% will be better.

Really good atmosphere and yummy foods. We were very happy with all foods. Super delicious Provoleta is apparently an traditional Argentinian dish and is like raclette. I would go back again for sure and would recommend friends.
Good steak with decent side dishes. Starters are large enough. Overall the quality of the food is very good. Prices are acceptable for a business lunch.

The food - starting with the provoleta, through to the steaks and sides, and finishing with desserts - was great; certainly one of the best steaks I've enjoyed in Hong Kong. However, we did have the misfortune of visiting at the same time as a large and boisterous party, which made conversation difficult, and the staff had their hands full, although when they did serve us they were very helpful and friendly. We would definitely be interested in returning at a quieter time and sampling more of their appealing menu.

出張帰りに寄った
香港でのディナーはアルゼンチンステーキのお店。

アルゼンチン料理🇦🇷って初めて食べた！

お店に着くまではなんだかちょっとセレブ〜なエリアで、デニムにTシャツの私はドレスコードにどきどき。無事入店出来て「ホッ」。

前菜はサーモンの和え物と、椰子の芽のサラダ。
ほんのりパクチーの香りがしたり、若干中華アレンジされてる感じだったけど、とってもとっても美味しい未知の味。椰子の芽があんなに甘いなんて…！

メインのステーキはフィレ肉を10オンス。焼き方はミディアム。表面がパリっとなる位香ばしくって、断面は綺麗な赤ピンク。どこを切っても美味しい！ソースが6種類あって、グリーントマトのソースがスパイシーで好きだな。半分位はなんのソースか分からなかったけど、菜っ葉のソース？も好き。

締めはベリーソースのチーズケーキ。上面に生キャラメルが薄くかかってて、ベリーの酸味がぴったり。

あぁ、おなかいっぱい
ご馳走さまでした。
결혼기념일 저녁을 이곳에서 보냈습니다. 은은한 조명과 조용하면서도 유쾌한 분위기 와인과 스테이크 모두 완벽했습니다. 다녀온지 1년이 지났지만 가끔 이곳을 이야기합니다. 홍콩여행에서 특별한 곳을 보내고 싶으시면 이곳을 추천합니다 !
補祝友人生日飯，斧頭扒味道很好，肉質感佳。我們還點了香腸、沙拉、阿根挺甜品，食物水準高，服務亦－流。服務員小姐知道我們全枱講廣東話，說工作以來講最多廣東話了！她還主動幫我們影相，感謝她啊~

result.name: Runway Hong Kong

reviews.text: Best Sheesha ever. Sanju was very hospitable and courteous.

Randomly picked Runway for a reunion dinner with my travel buddies, as it’s at a convenient location for all four of us.

We kicked start the dinner with two platters of wings. The wings were served fresh hot, and they were spicy even without the hot sauce on the side. I love the crispy skin, which wrapped juicy chicken meat underneath. Yum!

Cheese nachos were great too! They were not ordinary nachos crisps that you could get from supermarket, but legit thick ones. Crunchy, and cheese was smeared in between the nachos. The sour cream was great too! As for the brown sauce, we thought it’s something like hummus? Only complain is, the portion was a bit small for four people, and we finished the whole plate really quickly.

I requested for these mini burgers, and they were awesome! Buns were crunchy! We could hear some cracking sound when we cut the buns to share. The beef patties were very thick and juicy too! So delicious!

We saw attractive photo of these beef cubes looping on restaurant display, which got us to order one to try, and it did not disappoint! You could see the steam coming out of the hot plate in the photo! And the beef cubes were cooked right to the point, not too chewy, but quite tender and juicy indeed. The bell peppers made great seasoning and sides.

This carbonara might be ordinary, but it’s a great dish to share among the four of us. The creamy white sauce was so satisfying with the al dente spaghetti. Not to mention our all time comfort food - fatty bacon strips!

We ended the meal with Fish n Chips. Hum…I was expecting legit fish, not these fish fingers…Oh well, these fish fingers tasted good, but a bit too salty as there was salt sprinkled on top…Thin fries were gone really soon, they are always popular.

We also got some beer with Happy Hour deal (buy one get one free). And some of my friends were really interested in shisha. We might as well visit again during weekend to try out the nice smelling shisha.
Shisha is the best in the WORLD. And this coming from 3 people from 3 different countries where shisha is widely found.
best coctails nice shisha staff is very attentitave and helpfull always happy to accomandate all request chill  place will back  cheers 🍸🥃
Awesome place to hang out. Best Shisha in Hong Kong. Great friendly staff. Cant go wrong if you are looking for a nice night out (or a laid back early evening).
